unsigned afs_debug
 
: zero-terminated name

struct ubifs_dent_node - directory entry node. : common header : node key : target inode number : reserved for future, zeroes : type of the target inode (UBIFS_ITYPE_REG, UBIFS_ITYPE_DIR, etc) : name length : A 32bits random number, used to construct a 64bits identifier.

Note, do not forget to amend 'zero_dent_node_unused()' function when changing the padding fields.
